column2: The country of which the crop was harvested from. This includes every country from Europe including some regions from each country.
The year of which the crop was harvested to see the change in crop harvest. Ranges from 2009 - 2018.
This is one of three different ‘crops’; Grassland, Cereals and Dry pulses.
The amount of the crop harvested in the type.
The type in which the value was harvested. This is done in Hectares.
